	   <tr><td colspan=2>Hmm how misguided some people are...<br><br>It is a well known fact that wizards are a pain in the ass to solo until 29.<br><br>Myself into my 35th season now, found upto 16 hell, but dont get upset my friend, the power does come with time. Reach 29 and you'll find people are a lot more respectful to you. Basically anything to beg a port. BTW I solo'd 5-16 in Crushbone then to HH to get early twenties.<br><br>At 35 i am now finding players cant get enough of my circle of force spell, (200+ dmg to 5 targets) most mana efficent spell in game upto 51. <br><br>Or maybe my 310 dmg 263 dmg 250 dmg nukes would interest a group.<br><br>Bare with it as I say its a well known fact wizzys suck until 16.<br><br>Regards<br><br>Nattiny Cognizance<br>Leader of the Drunken Fishermen<br>Rodcet Nife Server<br>Gnome Wizard of the 35th season<br><br>BTW RACE is a huge issue in how effective a wizard is. As you know INT sets mana so pick a race with high int.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
